                        <description><![CDATA[<p>Mobile-first design ensures your website works well on all devices, starting with the smallest screens.</p><h2 id=why-mobile-first>Why Mobile-First?</h2><p>Most users access websites on mobile devices, so it makes sense to prioritize mobile experience.</p><h2 id=key-principles>Key Principles</h2><ul><li>Start with mobile layout</li><li>Use responsive breakpoints</li><li>Test on real devices</li></ul><h2 id=best-practices>Best Practices</h2><p>Always test your designs on actual mobile devices to ensure they work correctly.</p>]]></description>
